            "stanza_text": "Comme une ville qui s’allume\nEt que le vent vient embraser,\nTout mon cœur brûle et se consume,\nJ’ai soif, oh ! j’ai soif d’un baiser."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Baiser de la bouche et des lèvres",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Où notre amour vient se poser,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Plein de délices et de fièvres,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Ah ! j’ai soif, j’ai soif d’un baiser !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Baiser de la bouche et des lèvres\nOù notre amour vient se poser,\nPlein de délices et de fièvres,\nAh ! j’ai soif, j’ai soif d’un baiser !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Baiser multiplié que l’homme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Ne pourra jamais épuiser,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Ô toi, que tout mon être nomme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "J’ai soif, oui, j’ai soif d’un baiser.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Baiser multiplié que l’homme\nNe pourra jamais épuiser,\nÔ toi, que tout mon être nomme,\nJ’ai soif, oui, j’ai soif d’un baiser."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Fruit doux où la lèvre s’amuse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Beau fruit qui rit de s’écraser,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
